\c 63 Kutongwa kwam arudzi 63 1 Ndianiko uyu anobva Edhomu, anobva Bhozira ane nguo dzaka tsvuka kwazvo? Ndiani uyo akafuka zvinobwinya, anofamba noukuru hwesimba rake? "Ndini ndinotaura nokururama, ndine simba rokuponesa." 2 Ko nguo yenyu yakatsvuka nei? Zvokufuka zvenyu zvakafanana nezvomunhu anotsika muchisviniro chewaini neiko? 3 "Ini ndakatsika chisviniro chewaini ndoga; kwakanga kusina munhu wamarudzi avanhu aiva neni; zvirokwazvo, ndakavatsika pakutsamwa kwangu, ndakavapwanya pahasha dzangu; ropa ravo rikatsatikira panguo dzangu, ndikasvibisa zvokufuka zvangu zvose. 4 Nokuti ndakafunga zuva rokutsiva mumwoyo mangu; gore ravakadzikunurwa vangu rasvika. 5 Ndikatarira, ndikashayiwa anobatsira, ndikashamiswa nokuti kwakanga kusina anotsigira; naizvozvo ruoko rwangu rwakandivigira ruponeso, kutsamwa kwangu ndiko kwakanditsigira. 6 Ndikatsika-tsika marudzi avanhu pakutsamwa kwangu, ndikavapengesa nedoro rokutsamwa kwangu, ndikadurura ropa rohupenyu hwavo pasi." Vanhu vaJehovha vanokumbira kuti vanzwirwe nyasha 7 Ndicharumbidza hunyoro hwaJehovha namabasa aJehovha anofanira kuru
